cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with video analysis and annotation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the possibility of adversarial attacks on the video analysis system, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to manipulate the video analysis system, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
